theorem Topology.closure_eq_of_subset_subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A B : Set X} (hAB : A ⊆ B) (hBsubset : (B : Set X) ⊆ closure (A : Set X)) :
    closure (A : Set X) = closure (B : Set X) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · -- `closure A ⊆ closure B`
    have hSub : (A : Set X) ⊆ closure (B : Set X) :=
      Set.Subset.trans hAB subset_closure
    have h := closure_mono hSub
    simpa [closure_closure] using h
  · -- `closure B ⊆ closure A`
    exact closure_mono hBsubset
